---
import astroLogo from '../assets/astro.svg';
import background from '../assets/background.svg';
import AOS from 'aos';
import 'aos/dist/aos.css'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero-w-img text-black py-20 md:py-32 justify-center flex">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col gap-16" data-aos="fade-up">
		<div class="hero-img relative w-full h-full">
			<Image class="rounded w-full object-cover aspect-[2/1] md:aspect-[5/1] hero-img" src="http://static.photos/nature/1200x630/42" alt="Hero Image von Bergen" width="200" height="200"/>
			<div class="overlay absolute w-full h-full top-0 rounded"></div>
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6" data-aos="fade-up">
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-start">
				<p class="subheadline px-2">Alen's Bodenatelier</p>
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">Hochwertige Bodenlösungen für jedes Zuhause</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="w-[100%] md:w-[50%] flex flex-col gap-4 items-start">
				<p>Alen's Bodenatelier verbindet traditionelle Handwerkskunst mit modernem Stil und höchster Langlebigkeit – für Böden, die nicht nur schön aussehen, sondern auch Generationen überdauern.</p>
				<a href="#contact" class="bg-[var(--primary-trans)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)] text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition duration-300">Kostenloses Angebot anfordern</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- Services Section -->
<section id="services" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">Unsere Dienstleistungen</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <!-- Service 1 -->
            <div class="service-card bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="layers" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Parkettböden</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Premium-Parkettinstallation für zeitlose Eleganz und Langlebigkeit.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 2 -->
            <div class="service-card bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="box" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Laminat & Vinyl</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Preiswerte und stilvolle Bodenbeläge, die pflegeleicht sind.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 3 -->
            <div class="service-card bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="grid" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Fliesen & Naturstein</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Schöne und langlebige Fliesenlösungen für jeden Raum in Ihrem Zuhause.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 4 -->
            <div class="service-card bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="tool" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Aufbereitung & Reparaturen</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Wir bringen Ihre bestehenden Böden wieder in ihren ursprünglichen Zustand.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="py-16 bg-secondary">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 mb-8 lg:mb-0 lg:pr-12" data-aos="fade-right">
                <img src="http://static.photos/industry/640x360/89" alt="Alen bei der Arbeit" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full">
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2" data-aos="fade-left">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Über Alen</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">Mit jahrelanger Erfahrung im Bodenhandwerk legt Alen großen Wert auf zuverlässige, schöne und langlebige Ergebnisse.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Von kleinen Wohnprojekten bis zu großen Gewerbeflächen erhält jeder Boden die gleiche Liebe zum Detail und Qualitätsbewusstsein.</p>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <i data-feather="award" class="text-white w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Zertifizierter Bodenspezialist mit über 10 Jahren Erfahrung</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">Warum uns wählen</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Qualitätshandwerk</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Präzision und Liebe zum Detail bei jedem Projekt.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="shield" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Langlebige Materialien</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Wir verwenden nur Materialien höchster Qualität.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="users" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Persönlicher Service</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Maßgeschneiderte Lösungen, die auf Ihre Bedürfnisse abgestimmt sind.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="dollar-sign" class="text-white w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Transparente Preise</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Keine versteckten Gebühren – nur ehrliche Angebote.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Gallery Section -->
<section id="gallery" class="py-16 bg-secondary">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">Unsere Arbeiten</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="gallery-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <img src="http://static.photos/indoor/640x360/1" alt="Bodenprojekt" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <img src="http://static.photos/indoor/640x360/2" alt="Bodenprojekt" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <img src="http://static.photos/indoor/640x360/3" alt="Bodenprojekt" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                <img src="http://static.photos/indoor/640x360/4" alt="Bodenprojekt" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                <img src="http://static.photos/indoor/640x360/5" alt="Bodenprojekt" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                <img src="http://static.photos/indoor/640x360/6" alt="Bodenprojekt" class="rounded-lg w-full h-64 object-cover">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonials Section -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">Was unsere Kunden sagen</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">"Alen hat unser Wohnzimmer mit wunderschönen Parkettböden verwandelt. Seine Liebe zum Detail war beeindruckend!"</p>
                <p class="font-semibold">- Sarah M.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">"Professionell, pünktlich und perfekte Ergebnisse. Wir sind sehr zufrieden mit unserem neuen Küchenboden."</p>
                <p class="font-semibold">- Thomas K.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent mr-1"></i>
                    <i data-feather="star" class="text-accent"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">"Das Team hat unsere alten Parkettböden hervorragend aufgearbeitet. Sie sehen aus wie neu!"</p>
                <p class="font-semibold">- Elena P.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact Section -->
<section id="contact" class="py-16 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">Kontakt aufnehmen</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 mb-8 lg:mb-0 lg:pr-12" data-aos="fade-right">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Kontaktinformationen</h3>
                <div class="mb-6 flex items-start">
                    <i data-feather="mail" class="mr-4 mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold">E-Mail</h4>
                        <p>contact@alensbodenatelier.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-6 flex items-start">
                    <i data-feather="phone" class="mr-4 mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold">Telefon</h4>
                        <p>+1 (555) 123-4567</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-6 flex items-start">
                    <i data-feather="map-pin" class="mr-4 mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold">Servicebereich</h4>
                        <p>Wir bedienen die gesamte Metropolregion</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex space-x-4">
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-accent transition duration-300">
                        <i data-feather="facebook"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-accent transition duration-300">
                        <i data-feather="instagram"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-accent transition duration-300">
                        <i data-feather="linkedin"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2" data-aos="fade-left">
                <form class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-gray-700">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2" for="name">Name</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2" for="email">E-Mail</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2" for="phone">Telefon</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2" for="message">Nachricht</label>
                        <textarea id="message" rows="4" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-accent hover:bg-yellow-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300">Kostenlose Beratung anfordern</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>




<style>
	#background {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: -1;
		filter: blur(100px);
	}

	#container {
		font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
		height: 100%;
	}

	main {
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	#hero {
		display: flex;
		align-items: start;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 16px;
	}

	#links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 16px;
	}

	#links a {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 10px 12px;
		color: #111827;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	#links a:hover {
		color: rgb(78, 80, 86);
	}

	#links a svg {
		height: 1em;
		margin-left: 8px;
	}

	#links a.button {
		color: white;
		background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		box-shadow:
			inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12),
			inset 0 -2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
		border-radius: 10px;
	}

	#links a.button:hover {
		color: rgb(230, 230, 230);
		box-shadow: none;
	}

	pre {
		font-family:
			ui-monospace, 'Cascadia Code', 'Source Code Pro', Menlo, Consolas, 'DejaVu Sans Mono',
			monospace;
		font-weight: normal;
		background: linear-gradient(14deg, #d83333 0%, #f041ff 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin: 0;
	}

	code {
		display: inline-block;
		background:
			linear-gradient(66.77deg, #f3cddd 0%, #f5cee7 100%) padding-box,
			linear-gradient(155deg, #d83333 0%, #f041ff 18%, #f5cee7 45%) border-box;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		padding: 6px 8px;
	}

	.box {
		padding: 16px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid white;
	}

	#news {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 16px;
		right: 16px;
		max-width: 300px;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: background 0.2s;
		backdrop-filter: blur(50px);
	}

	#news:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
	}

	@media screen and (max-height: 368px) {
		#news {
			display: none;
		}
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
		#container {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		#hero {
			display: block;
			padding-top: 10%;
		}

		#links {
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		#links a.button {
			padding: 14px 18px;
		}

		#news {
			right: 16px;
			left: 16px;
			bottom: 2.5rem;
			max-width: 100%;
		}

		h1 {
			line-height: 1.5;
		}
	}

	        .hero-bg {
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(1, 50, 32, 0.6), rgba(1, 50, 32, 0.6)), url('http://static.photos/nature/1200x630/42');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .gallery-item {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .gallery-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }
</style>
